{"type": "article", "id": 34414, "title": "Moschino加大中国投入，以及，《新世纪福音战士》字体出售 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-14T02:30:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 34830, "name": "珠宝展"}, {"id": 34831, "name": "纽约街头潮牌"}, {"id": 3321, "name": "Stella McCartney"}, {"id": 11892, "name": "Aeffe"}, {"id": 29129, "name": "Superdry"}, {"id": 34832, "name": "Chinatown Market"}, {"id": 34833, "name": "Desigual"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/201611141015133FofvbEmpgtD1rna.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/desigual-q3-revenues-2016-sales-down-declining-tourism-10704315/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>受法国旅游业衰退的影响，Desigual 第三季度营收下滑</b></a> | 据西班牙服装品牌 Desigual 称，受法国旅游业衰退的影响，它在法国地区的销售下滑，此外，意大利和德国的销售也有所下滑。虽然 Desigual 并未透露它在第三季度的具体营收，不过，它在九月份的营收下降了 6.8%，至 6.752 亿欧元。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-11-10/superdry-owner-surges-as-label-leaves-retail-rivals-trailing\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国潮牌 Superdry 的母公司上半年业绩大涨</b></a> | 截止至 10 月 29 日的六个月里，Superdry 的母公司 SuperGroup 的销售额同比增长 31.1%，至 3.34 亿英镑。电商销售额增长 25%，至 2.152 亿英镑。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/moschino-drives-aeffe-profits-in-nine-month-period-10702839/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Moschino 的母公司平稳增长，计划在中国开更多新店</b></a> | 截止至 9 月 30 日的前九个月，拥有 Moschino、Alberta Ferretti 和 Pollini 等多个品牌的意大利奢侈品集团 Aeffe SpA 的销售额平稳增长了 3.8%，净利润增长超过 200%，至 490 万欧元。据该集团的首席财务官 Marcello Tassinari 称，配件的表现越来越好，尤其是 Moschino 的配件，整个公司的配件销售额已经占到总销售额的 40%。而中国市场的良好表现，抵消了公司在日本市场的销售下降。到今年年底，Aeffe 在中国的销售额有望增加到 11%－12%，在明年，计划在中国进一步开 5-10 家新店，主要是 Moschino 品牌。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>由 D &amp; DEPARTMENT PROJECT 团队运营，将于 12 月 8 日在东京涩谷 Hikarie 举办的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/47-accessories-2-47-accessories\" rel=\"nofollow\">「47 accessories 2-47 都道府县 accessories 展-」</a>饰品展，汇聚了来自日本各个都道府县，创意与工艺结合的饰品，还挺有意思的。有机会的话，可以去看看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085335jDCGniFN5gJs94d3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085343AU0K1mDRnjlJNFd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085343pZsIu602jn9PKWez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085343sx7V6ACkyGOjZWwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611140853504PpuVWMsnL0lUBSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/12/chinatown-market-2016-fall-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chinatown Market </a>是来自纽约的华裔设计师 Michael Cherman 和 LA 的摄影师 Alexander Bortz 共同创立的新锐品牌，它表达纽约的 Canal Street 的街头潮流文化，从帽子到 T-shirt 的系列单品都还不错。价格也很适合年轻人，从 30 美元到 40 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111408523212nriJoR4jfCwS7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611140852323C7tQFYM4VmJBDuN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085244dnTv768NzSBMof15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085245JNoXp3cPWET7dKM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085245W8SX9ycBLuZjJnra.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085245aR8dlXZptYQTw9E0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085245kPO5NmJBQMg3Hqb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085255clJmH8tbfgAWTU2k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611140852553MHUpd6zCNGF0xPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085303AdIpQ1v5iVCx9lrw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">字体变得越来越受欢迎，连《新世纪福音战士》的字体也要出售了。这款字体是自 1995 年开播以后就有的原创字体，现在《新世界福音战士》的官方网站准备出售当中所用的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/583115\" rel=\"nofollow\">「新世纪福音战士官方字体 Matisse EB」</a>，分为个人版及商业版进行分别出售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085704vU9lGHYCX41eoabM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085712Djlc9ymbg6qxCvK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">加拿大人气歌手 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/the-weeknd-xo-2016-fall-winter-second-drop\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Weeknd 个人品牌 XO 发布 2016 秋冬第二波新品</a>，灵感来自街头涂鸦和丝网印刷，并带来了连帽衫、T-shirt、运动裤等多款单品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085729sl7DhXEozgLRtkUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085741JF9RajYpInVwEPeH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085742aSKRxljb71CeJ4dH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085743TwlcVBhmgD2yGJfk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085743XvfblRoDUu0O5Shz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611140857435E6xwS3oyZ0gNAb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085743PNRMXnvzgyTxuFLW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085752DaMA5lESIpmdzoXb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085752YPfdFbw15JGtiKql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>伦敦品牌<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/12/stella-mccartney-first-menswear/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Stella McCartney </a>今年新动作不断。先是首次进军香水市场，后又与 adidas 合作推限量款。最近，Stella McCartney 推出了它的首个男装系列，来看看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085803oyzAgwKvjOqHdYB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085813fQjHNnrb9OW65mIx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085813jdLXwADYWJ0qhnGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114085813LfHMSC5g1xpB